FSter - Configurable virtual filesystem for Tracker
===============================================================================

FSter is a virtual filesystem built on FUSE, able to dispose contents fetched
from Tracker according to a flexible XML configuration.

Documentation Wiki: http://gitorious.org/itsme/pages/Fster
Developers' Mailing List: http://lists.itsme.it/mailman/listinfo/itsme-dev
Bugtracker: http://bugs.itsme.it/

REQUIREMENTS
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
FSter depends on:

  - fuse >= 2.8.1
  - tracker-client >= 0.7.11
  - libxml2 >= 2.7.4

INSTALLATION
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
See INSTALL file.

